headline: Thermo Fisher (NYSE:TMO) Posts Better-Than-Expected Sales In Q4 CY2025
summary: Life sciences company Thermo Fisher (NYSE:TMO) reported Q4 CY2025 results beating Wall Street’s revenue expectations, with sales up 7.2% year on year to $12.22 billion. Its non-GAAP profit of $6.57 per share was 1.9% above analysts’ consensus estimates.
